headline: Duke Energy (DUK) Q2 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: Duke Energy (DUK) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +5.04% and +2.35%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
